teams/
├── frontend.md         - Frontend team prompt and configuration
├── backend.md          - Backend team prompt and configuration
├── database.md         - Database team prompt and configuration
├── testing.md          - Testing team prompt and configuration
└── token-optimization.md - Token optimization team prompt and configuration

Each team file contains:
1. Team role and responsibilities
2. Capabilities and constraints
3. Tools and access levels
4. Work process and approval flow
5. Token limits and budget
6. Reporting format
